global_events.message:
Terminid spores have engulfed Heeth and Angel's Venture, spawning hordes of Terminids that overwhelmed our colonial militias. Clearly, the bug hive instinct oriented their mindless expansion towards dishonouring the memory of those who fought to free these planets.

Your fellow Helldivers paid for these lands with their lives. We cannot lose them now. Hold the planets until SEAF reinforcements arrive.
global_events.title: hologram_major_order_sub_header_introduction

global_events.message: Well done, Helldivers. SEAF Containment Teams will take over cleanup and inoculation operations from here. Colonists have been advised that there is absolutely zero threat of further Terminid violence, and to settle their families with total peace of mind. Additionally, the pilots allocated to spore clearance on Veld have now been redirected to Helldiver support operations. Extraction will be faster on all operations.
global_events.title: hologram_major_order_sub_header_outcome_success

global_events.message:
Despite the valorous efforts of the Helldivers, Automaton marauders have invaded Super Earth territory. Patriotic citizens mourn as their sufficiently-sized homes burn to the ground.

Super Earth citizens demand justice, and they will receive it.
global_events.title: hologram_major_order_sub_header_outcome_failure
